ppendPart<openparen>face<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.feature.setGeometry<openparen>sidewall<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.feature.setAttribute<openparen><apos>__ssc.type<apos><comma><space><apos>side<apos><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.pyoutput<openparen>self.feature<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>planarBoundaries.append<openparen>planarBoundaries<openbracket>0<closebracket><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>planar<space>=<space>fmeobjects.FMEPolygon<openparen>fmeobjects.FMELine<openparen>planarBoundaries<closeparen><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.feature.setGeometry<openparen>planar<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.feature.setAttribute<openparen><apos>__ssc.type<apos><comma><space><apos>planar<apos><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.pyoutput<openparen>self.feature<closeparen> }    OUTPUT { PYOUTPUT FEATURE_TYPE "$(BRepSolidBoundaryCreator.Beta_WORKSPACE_NAME)_PythonCaller_2_OUTPUT"         }
